	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I think it's really neat that you can accomplish simple affine transformations just by using Offsets Per Tile mode, combined with X scrolling.  I never would have thought that this would work so well.
<br />
<br />Looks like angles can range between -7.125 and 7.125 degrees before seeing artifacts from being too steep.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


